    %h2 Gold Rush &amp; Carnival Night

    %p
      Gold Rush is an afternoon long event that encompasses the entirety of camp
      == in a frantic search for gold. The more gold a #{link_to 'cabin', '/tour/cabins.html'} finds, the more &ldquo;money&rdquo;
      they get to use for carnival night, a huge end-of-session celebration
      ending in a display of fireworks.

  .shadow.rounded.video= vimeo 31705723, 6

