      It is a massive, whole camp, relay race that spans every activity area from
      == the #{link_to 'waterfront', '/tour/waterfront.html'} to the
      == #{link_to 'Challenge Course', '/tour/challenge-course.html'} to the
      == #{link_to 'athletic fields', '/tour/sports.html'}.

