    %h2 Olympic Day

    %p
      Olympic Day is an entire day set aside for the colors war, called BROG.
      == It has just about every game imaginable from #{link_to 'Riflery', '/tour/riflery-skeet.html'} to fooz ball and
      == #{link_to 'climbing', '/tour/challenge-course.html'} to sand castle building. Every event is worth points for your team
      and bonus points are to be had for spectacular feats or good sportsmanship!

